1.            Goto the Collaborate Tab --> "Reconcile Hosting"
2.            Under the "Orphaned Elements"  dropdown
3.            Navigate to your specific devices
4.            Here you can right click on a device and select a new host or delete the element.
5.            You can also find where it is located by typing the "ID number" located at the end of the device name.
6.            Goto Manage Tab --> Under "Inquiry" select "Select by ID" and type the ID number of the device or
                select the device itself and them select "IDs of Selection" copy the ID number then select "select by ID"
                again and paste the number then press "show"
